author: IANS
title: 'Bajrangi Bhaijaan' to release in Romania
text:
Salman Khan-starrer 'Bajrangi Bhaijaan' will hit theatres in Romania tomorrow.

'Bajrangi Bhaijaan' 
The blockbuster will release across 14 screens with Romanian subtitles. The Romanian poster designs of 'Bajrangi Bhaijaan' will also be attached.
Directed by Kabir Khan, the film also stars Kareena Kapoor Khan and Nawazuddin Siddiqui in prominent roles.
'Bajrangi Bhaijaan' released in India on July 17 and is produced by Salman Khan, Rockline Venkatesh and distributed worldwide by Eros International.
